--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PART 2: DATA CLEANING & REFORMATTING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* 1. generate date_clean = date(date, "DMY")
(18,249 missing values generated)


. format date_clean %td

. label variable date_clean "Cleaned Date"


* 2. Rename PLU columns to safe names if they imported with leading numbers
. capture rename v5 plu_4046

. capture rename v6 plu_4225

. capture rename v7 plu_4770


* 3. Handle any potential structural missing values safely
. misstable summarize averageprice totalvolume totalbags type region
(variables nonmissing or string)


* 4. Drop unnecessary index columns if present (like the leading row index column B)
. capture drop v1


* 5. Save clean data framework
. save "avocado_cleaned.dta", replace
(file avocado_cleaned.dta not found)
file avocado_cleaned.dta saved
